little longer if you don't mind.

267
00:15:04,148 --> 00:15:05,471
Yeah. Of course.

268
00:15:05,668 --> 00:15:06,694
You sure?

269
00:15:07,511 --> 00:15:08,552
Yeah, I'm sure.

270
00:15:08,587 --> 00:15:10,991
Looks like you owe
these folks a rematch.

271
00:15:11,708 --> 00:15:14,051
So, um...
I will see you when I see you.

272
00:15:30,524 --> 00:15:31,882
- To Jake.
- To Jake.

273
00:15:32,807 --> 00:15:35,697
